<taxonomicName authority="Walsingham, 1907" authorityName="Walsingham" authorityYear="1907" box="[563,625,1052,1076]" class="Insecta" family="Blastobasidae" genus="Hypatopa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="limae">
<emphasis box="[563,625,1052,1076]" italics="true" pageId="91" pageNumber="92">limae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is derived from the Latin meaning, labor.
</paragraph>
